00:19:27.042 --> 00:19:28.835
No, that's not...

261
00:19:31.421 --> 00:19:32.714
Phil's really nice.

262
00:19:46.227 --> 00:19:48.938
It's met a phase.
You want to check it?

263
00:19:50.440 --> 00:19:51.816
I believe you.

264
00:19:52.817 --> 00:19:55.236
Why didn't you move
with your mother and Phil?

265
00:19:57.906 --> 00:20:04.746
Well, Phil's a minor league baseball
