266
00:20:04.829 --> 00:20:08.208
and my mom stayed home with me,
but I knew it made her unhappy,

267
00:20:08.291 --> 00:20:13.213
so I figured I'd stay
with my dad for a while.

268
00:20:14.798 --> 00:20:16.091
And now you're unhappy?

269
00:20:17.550 --> 00:20:18.593
No.

270
00:20:18.676 --> 00:20:22.180
I'm sorry, I'm just...
