found them hunting on our land.

483
00:34:14.511 --> 00:34:16.722
But they claimed to be
something different,

484
00:34:16.805 --> 00:34:19.058
SO we made a treaty with them.

485
00:34:19.141 --> 00:34:22.186
If they promised to stay
off Quileute lands,

486
00:34:22.269 --> 00:34:26.523
then we wouldn't expose
what they really were to the palefaces.

487
00:34:27.816 --> 00:34:29.109
I thought they just moved here.

488
00:34:30.861 --> 00:34:32.363
Or just moved back.

489
00:34:33.572 --> 00:34:34.740
Right.

490
00:34:34.823 --> 00:34:38.452
It touched my hand.
A snake! Stop!

491
00:34:40.162 --> 00:34:44.083
- Well, what are they really?
- It's just a story, Bella.

492
00:34:45.793 --> 00:34:47.044
Come on, let's go.

493
00:34:50.839 --> 00:34:53.133
A shake!

